DiabloCalc.skilltips||(DiabloCalc.skilltips={}),DiabloCalc.passivetips||(DiabloCalc.passivetips={}),DiabloCalc.skilltips.crusader={akaratschampion:{a:'<p>Dealing damage burns enemies with the power of Akarat, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">460%</span> weapon damage as Fire over <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>29</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Increases the bonus Wrath regeneration from Akarat\'s Champion to <span class="d3-color-green">10</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>34</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Using Akarat\'s Champion reduces the remaining cooldown of your other abilities by <span class="d3-color-green">12</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>42</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">150%</span> additional Armor while Akarat\'s Champion is active.</p><p>The first time you take fatal damage while Akarat\'s Champion is active, you will be returned to full health.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>49</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> increased attack speed while Akarat\'s Champion is active.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>58</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"phy",c:"lit",d:"hol",e:"hol",x:"fir"},icon:3024819679,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3024819679\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">90</span> seconds</p><p>Explode with the power of your order, increasing your damage by <span class="d3-color-green">35%</span> and increasing your Wrath regeneration by <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> seconds.</p> <p class="special">Conviction</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>25</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},blessedhammer:{a:'<p>The hammer is engulfed in fire and has a <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span> chance to scorch the ground over which it passes. Enemies who pass through the scorched ground take <span class="d3-color-green">330%</span> weapon damage as Fire per second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>18</em>.</p>',b:'<p>The hammer is charged with lightning that occasionally arcs between you and the hammer as it spirals through the air, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span> weapon damage as Lightning to enemies caught in the arcs. </p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>22</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Increase the damage of Blessed Hammer to <span class="d3-color-green">640%</span> weapon damage as Holy and increase its area of effect by <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>35</em>.</p>',d:'<p>The hammer Slows enemies it passes through and has a <span class="d3-color-green">35%</span> chance to explode on impact, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">460%</span> weapon damage as Physical and Stunning enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> yards for <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>48</em>.</p>',e:'<p>The Hammer now orbits you as you move.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>57</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"lit",c:"hol",d:"phy",e:"hol",x:"hol"},icon:2047437116,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2047437116\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> Wrath</p><p>Summon a blessed hammer that spins around you, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">320%</span> weapon damage as Holy to all enemies hit.</p> <p class="special">Secondary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>12</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},blessedshield:{a:'<p>The shield becomes charged with lightning and has a <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span> chance to Stun the first enemy hit for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds. Each enemy hit after the first has a <span class="d3-color-green">5%</span> reduced chance to be Stunned.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>24</em>.</p>',b:'<p>The shield erupts in flames and has a <span class="d3-color-green">33%</span> chance to explode on impact, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">310%</span> weapon damage as Fire to all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>29</em>.</p>',c:'<p>When the shield hits an enemy, your Armor is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">5%</span> and Life regeneration is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">5%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>38</em>.</p>',d:'<p>When the shield hits an enemy, it splits into <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> small fragments that bounce between nearby enemies, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">170%</span> weapon damage as Holy to all enemies hit.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>44</em>.</p>',e:'<p>The shield no longer bounces, but pierces through all enemies with a <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> chance to knock them aside.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>59</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"lit",b:"fir",c:"phy",d:"hol",e:"hol",x:"hol"},icon:3505549997,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3505549997\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> Wrath</p><p>Hurl your shield, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">430%</span> weapon damage as Holy plus <span class="d3-color-green">250%</span> of shield Block Chance as Holy damage. The shield will ricochet to <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> nearby enemies.</p> <p>Requires <span class="value">Shield</span></p> <p class="special">Secondary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>20</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},bombardment:{a:'<p>In place of the burning spheres, barrels of spikes are hurled. Damage of each barrel is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">200%</span> of your Thorns.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>63</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Each impact has a <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> Critical Hit Chance.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>65</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Each impact scatters <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> mines onto the battlefield that explode when enemies walk near them, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">160%</span> weapon damage as Fire to all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>67</em>.</p>',d:'<p>A single, much larger ball of explosive pitch is hurled at the targeted location dealing <span class="d3-color-green">3320%</span> weapon damage to all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">18</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>69</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Instead of randomly finding targets nearby, the bombardment will continue to fall on your initial target.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>70</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"fir",c:"fir",d:"phy",e:"hol",x:"phy"},icon:1417711558,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1417711558\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">60</span> seconds</p><p>Call in an assault from afar, raining <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> spheres of burning pitch and stone onto enemies around you, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">2850%</span> total weapon damage to enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">12</span> yards of the impact zone.</p> <p class="special">Conviction</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>61</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},condemn:{a:'<p><span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> of all damage taken while the explosion is building is added to the damage of the explosion.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>56</em>.</p>',b:'<p>As the explosion charges up, it sucks in enemies. The closer it is to exploding, the more enemies it sucks in.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>26</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Reduce the cooldown by <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second for each enemy hit by the explosion.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>38</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Increase the damage radius to <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>47</em>.</p>',e:'<p>The explosion now unleashes instantly.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>33</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"hol",c:"hol",d:"phy",e:"hol",x:"hol"},icon:3346730045,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3346730045\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> seconds</p><p>Build up a massive explosion, unleashing it after <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">1160%</span> weapon damage as Holy to all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> yards.</p> <p class="special">Utility</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>21</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},consecration:{a:'<p>The edge of the consecrated ground is surrounded by a sacred shield, preventing enemies from moving through it.</p><p>The duration of the consecration is reduced to <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>39</em>.</p>',b:'<p>The consecrated ground becomes covered in nails. Enemies that walk into the area take <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> of your Thorns damage every second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>29</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Increase the radius of the consecrated ground to <span class="d3-color-green">24</span> yards and increase the amount you and your allies heal for to <span class="d3-color-green">48278</span> Life per second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>23</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Enemies standing on consecrated ground take <span class="d3-color-green">155%</span> weapon damage as Fire per second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>46</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Enemies standing on consecrated ground have a <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> chance to be Feared for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>53</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"hol",b:"phy",c:"hol",d:"fir",e:"hol",x:"hol"},icon:663260264,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/663260264\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> seconds</p><p>Consecrate the ground <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> yards around you for <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> seconds. You and your allies heal for <span class="d3-color-green">32185</span> Life per second while standing on the consecrated ground.</p> <p class="special">Defensive</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>16</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},fallingsword:{a:'<p>The ground you fall on becomes superheated for <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">310%</span> weapon damage as Fire per second to all enemies who pass over it.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>24</em>.</p>',b:'<p>You build a storm of lightning as you fall which covers the area you land on for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds. Lightning strikes random enemies under the cloud, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">605%</span> weapon damage as Lightning and Stunning them for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>28</em>.</p>',c:'<p>You land with such force that <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> Avatars of the Order are summoned forth to fight by your side for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds. Each Avatar attacks for <span class="d3-color-green">280%</span> of your weapon damage as Physical.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>38</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Reduce the cooldown by <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second for each enemy hit by Falling Sword.  The cooldown cannot be reduced below <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>50</em>.</p>',e:'<p>A flurry of swords is summoned at the impact location, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">230%</span> weapon damage as Holy, hurling enemies around and incapacitating them for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>56</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"lit",c:"phy",d:"lit",e:"hol",x:"phy"},icon:2440240234,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2440240234\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">25</span> Wrath<br/><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> seconds</p><p>Launch yourself into the heavens and come crashing down on your enemies, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">1700%</span> weapon damage to everything within <span class="d3-color-green">14</span> yards of where you land.</p><p><span class="d3-color-yellow">This ability does not start its cooldown until after its effects expire.</span></p> <p class="special">Conviction</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>19</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},fistoftheheavens:{a:'<p>Summon a fiery storm that covers a <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> yard radius for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> weapon damage as Fire every second to enemies who pass underneath it.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>36</em>.</p>',b:'<p>The bolt detonates with a shockwave on impact, causing all enemies hit to be knocked away from the blast and Slowed by <span class="d3-color-green">80%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>47</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Creates a fissure of lightning energy that deals <span class="d3-color-green">410%</span> weapon damage as Lightning over <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds to nearby enemies. If there is another fissure nearby, lightning will arc between them dealing an additional <span class="d3-color-green">135%</span> weapon damage as Lightning with each arc.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>42</em>.</p>',d:'<p>The holy bolts crackle with holy lightning and zap enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">18</span> yards as they travel, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">40%</span> weapon damage as Holy.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>32</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Hurl a fist of Holy power that pierces through your enemies, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">270%</span> weapon damage as Holy, and exploding at your target, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">435%</span> weapon damage as Holy to enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> yards.</p><p>The explosion creates <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> piercing charged bolts that crawl outward, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">185%</span> weapon damage as Holy to enemies through whom they pass.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>54</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"lit",c:"lit",d:"hol",e:"hol",x:"lit"},icon:3114805186,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3114805186\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> Wrath</p><p>Call forth a pillar of lightning from the heavens that explodes, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">545%</span> weapon damage as Lightning to any enemy within <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> yards. The explosion creates <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> piercing charged bolts that arc outward and deal <span class="d3-color-green">255%</span> weapon damage as Lightning.</p> <p class="special">Secondary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>26</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},heavensfury:{a:'<p>The ray of Holy power grows to encompass <span class="d3-color-green">12</span> yards, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">2766%</span> weapon damage as Holy over <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds to enemies caught within it.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>36</em>.</p>',b:'<p>The ground touched by the ray becomes blessed, scorching it and dealing <span class="d3-color-green">1550%</span> weapon damage over <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds to enemies who walks through.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>31</em>.</p>',c:'<p>The ray splits into <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> smaller beams, each dealing <span class="d3-color-green">1980%</span> weapon damage as Holy over <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>44</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Ground touched by the ray pulses with power for <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds, stopping enemies who try to pass over it.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>52</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Call down a furious ray of Holy power that is focused through you in a beam across the battlefield, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">960%</span> weapon damage as Holy to all enemies it hits.</p><p>The cooldown is removed. Now costs <span class="d3-color-green">40</span> Wrath.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>62</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"hol",b:"hol",c:"hol",d:"lit",e:"hol",x:"hol"},icon:2946852966,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2946852966\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> seconds</p><p>Call down a furious ray of Holy power that deals <span class="d3-color-green">1710%</span> weapon damage as Holy over <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds to all enemies caught within it.</p> <p class="special">Conviction</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>30</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},ironskin:{a:'<p>Your metal skin is electrified, giving you a <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> chance to Stun enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> yards for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>44</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Increase the duration to <span class="d3-color-green">7</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>21</em>.</p>',c:'<p>When Iron Skin expires the metal explodes off, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">1400%</span> weapon damage to enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">12</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>32</em>.</p>',d:'<p>While active, your Thorns is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">300%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>14</em>.</p>',e:'<p>If you take damage while Iron Skin is active, your movement speed is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds and you can move through enemies unhindered.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>56</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"lit",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"lit",x:"phy"},icon:3165782921,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3165782921\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> seconds</p><p>Your skin turns to iron, absorbing <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> of all incoming damage for <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds.</p> <p class="special">Defensive</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>8</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},judgment:{a:'<p>For every enemy upon whom you pass judgment, you heal for <span class="d3-color-green">2682</span> Life per second for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>27</em>.</p>',b:'<p>All enemies are drawn toward the center of the judged area.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>31</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Increase the duration of the Immobilize to <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>37</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Damage dealt to judged enemies has an <span class="d3-color-green">8%</span> increased chance to be a Critical Hit.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>43</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Enemies in the judged area deal <span class="d3-color-green">40%</span> reduced damage for <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>59</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:2747472303,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2747472303\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> seconds</p><p>Pass judgment on all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> yards of the targeted location, Immobilizing them in place for <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds.</p> <p class="special">Defensive</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>22</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},justice:{a:'<p>Hurl a sword of justice at your enemies. When the sword hits an enemy, gain <span class="d3-color-green">5%</span> increased movement speed for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds. This effect stacks up to <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> times.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>48</em>.</p>',b:'<p>When the hammer hits an enemy, there is an <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> chance it will crack into <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> smaller hammers that fly out and deal <span class="d3-color-green">245%</span> weapon damage as Holy.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>31</em>.</p>',c:'<p>The hammer seeks out nearby targets and deal <span class="d3-color-green">335%</span> weapon damage.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>40</em>.</p>',d:'<p>The hammer is charged with lightning and explodes on impact, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span> weapon damage as Lightning to all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> yards. Enemies caught in the explosion have a <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> chance to be stunned for <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>22</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Throw a bolt of holy power that heals you and your allies for <span class="d3-color-green">2146</span> - <span class="d3-color-green">3219</span> Life when it hits an enemy.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>60</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"hol",c:"phy",d:"lit",e:"hol",x:"hol"},icon:1031678231,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1031678231\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Generate:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> Wrath per attack</p><p>Hurl a hammer of justice at your enemies, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">245%</span> weapon damage.</p> <p class="special">Primary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>15</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},lawsofhope:{a:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Empowering the Law also increases movement speed for you and your allies by <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span>, and allows everyone affected to run through enemies unimpeded.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>31</em>.</p>',b:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Empowering the Law also increases the maximum Life of you and your allies by <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>34</em>.</p>',c:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Empowering the Law also reduces all Physical damage taken by <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>40</em>.</p>',d:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Empowering the Law also heals you and your allies for <span class="d3-color-green">1073</span> Life for every point of Wrath that you spend. </p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>48</em>.</p>',e:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Empowering the Law also reduces all non-Physical damage taken by <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>58</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:3072384440,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3072384440\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> seconds</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Empower the Law, surrounding you and your allies in a shield for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds that absorbs up to <span class="d3-color-green">124128</span> damage.</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Recite the Law, healing you and your allies for <span class="d3-color-green">10728</span> Life per second.</p><p><span class="d3-color-yellow">Only one Law may be active at a time.</span></p> <p class="special">Laws</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>24</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},lawsofjustice:{a:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Empowering the Law also redirects <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> of the damage taken by your allies to you for the next <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>23</em>.</p>',b:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Empowering the Law also increases Armor for you and your allies by <span class="d3-color-green">7000</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>30</em>.</p>',c:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Empowering the Law also surrounds you and your allies with shields of faith for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds. The shields absorb up to <span class="d3-color-green">26821</span> damage.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>37</em>.</p>',d:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> While the Law is empowered, any enemy who attacks you or your allies will have their damage reduced by <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds, stacking up to a maximum of <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>43</em>.</p>',e:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Empowering the Law also grants immunity to control impairing effects to you and your allies for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>57</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:2430907811,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2430907811\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> seconds</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Empower the Law, granting you and your allies <span class="d3-color-green">490</span> increased resistance to all elements for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Recite the Law, granting you and your allies <span class="d3-color-green">140</span> increased resistance to all elements.</p><p><span class="d3-color-yellow">Only one Law may be active at a time.</span></p> <p class="special">Laws</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>17</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},lawsofvalor:{a:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Empowering the Law also increases your Life on Hit by <span class="d3-color-green">21457</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>21</em>.</p>',b:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Empowering the Law also grants you a <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> chance to Stun all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> yards for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>25</em>.</p>',c:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Empowering the Law also increases your Critical Hit Damage by <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>33</em>.</p>',d:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Empowering the law also reduces the Wrath cost of all skills by <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>45</em>.</p>',e:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> While the Law is empowered, each enemy killed increases the duration by <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second, up to a maximum of <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> seconds of increased time.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>54</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:3531549488,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3531549488\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> seconds</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Empower the Law, granting you and your allies <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> increased Attack Speed for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Recite the Law, granting you and your allies <span class="d3-color-green">8%</span> increased Attack Speed.</p><p><span class="d3-color-yellow">Only one Law may be active at a time.</span></p> <p class="special">Laws</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>14</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},phalanx:{a:'<p>The summoned avatars no longer march forward, but will wield bows and attack enemies, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">185%</span> weapon damage. These bowmen follow you as you move for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p><p>The Bowmen can only be summoned once every <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>30</em>.</p>',b:'<p>The summoned avatars charge the target and perform a shield bash, dealing an additional <span class="d3-color-green">180%</span> weapon damage to enemies at that location.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>35</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Summon warhorses that deal <span class="d3-color-green">490%</span> weapon damage and have a <span class="d3-color-green">30%</span> chance to Stun enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>43</em>.</p>',d:'<p>The avatars no longer walk forward, but stand at the summoned location, blocking all enemies from moving through.</p><p>The Avatars can only be summoned once every <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>49</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Instead of sending the avatars out away from you, you summon <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> Avatars of the Order to protect you and fight by your side for <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> seconds. Each Avatar will attack for <span class="d3-color-green">560%</span> of your weapon damage as Physical.</p><p>The Avatars can only be summoned once every <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>64</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:1729162028,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1729162028\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> Wrath</p><p>Summon powerful avatars who charge forward to the targeted destination. Enemies caught in the charge path take <span class="d3-color-green">490%</span> weapon damage.</p> <p class="special">Utility</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>27</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},provoke:{a:'<p>For each enemy successfully taunted, you gain <span class="d3-color-green">1073</span> additional Life on Hit for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.  </p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>15</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Provoke no longer taunts, but instead causes enemies to flee in Fear for <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>23</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Taunted enemies have their attack speed reduced by <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> and movement speed Slowed by <span class="d3-color-green">80%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>32</em>.</p>',d:'<p>For <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds after casting Provoke, any damage you deal will also deal <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> weapon damage as Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>40</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> increased Block Chance for <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds after casting Provoke.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>50</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"lit",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:3052489254,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3052489254\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> seconds<br/><span class="d3-color-gold">Generate:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> Wrath</p><p>Taunt all nearby enemies and instantly generate an additional <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> Wrath for every enemy taunted. Taunted enemies will focus their attention on you for <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds.</p> <p class="special">Utility</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>9</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},punish:{a:'<p>When you block with Hardened Senses active, you deal <span class="d3-color-green">140%</span> weapon damage as Holy to the attacker.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>45</em>.</p>',b:'<p>When you block with Hardened Senses active, you gain <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> increased Attack Speed for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>17</em>.</p>',c:'<p>When you block with Hardened Senses active, you gain <span class="d3-color-green">12874</span> increased Life regeneration for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>26</em>.</p>',d:'<p>When you block with Hardened Senses active, you explode with fury dealing <span class="d3-color-green">75%</span> weapon damage as Fire to enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>6</em>.</p>',e:'<p>When you block with Hardened Senses active, you gain <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> increased Critical Hit Chance for your next attack.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>52</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"hol",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"fir",e:"lit",x:"phy"},icon:2997083095,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2997083095\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Generate:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> Wrath per attack</p><p>Strike your enemy for <span class="d3-color-green">335%</span> weapon damage and gain Hardened Senses, increasing your Block Chance by <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p>Requires <span class="value">Shield</span></p> <p class="special">Primary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>1</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},shieldbash:{a:'<p>Increases the weapon damage of Shield bash to <span class="d3-color-green">875%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>39</em>.</p>',b:'<p>The shield shatters into other smaller fragments, hitting more enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">740%</span> weapon damage plus <span class="d3-color-green">335%</span> of your shield Block Chance as damage.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>7</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Additional shields erupt from you in a cross formation. Enemies hit by any of the additional shields take <span class="d3-color-green">155%</span> weapon damage plus <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> of your shield Block Chance as damage.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>27</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Shield Bash will now deal <span class="d3-color-green">1320%</span> weapon damage plus <span class="d3-color-green">500%</span> shield Block Chance as damage. The range is reduced to <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>53</em>.</p>',e:'<p>The targeted monster is stunned for <span class="d3-color-green">1.5</span> seconds. All other monsters hit are knocked back.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>15</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"hol",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"lit",x:"hol"},icon:1249306807,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1249306807\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> Wrath</p><p>Charge at your enemy, bashing him and all nearby foes. Deals <span class="d3-color-green">700%</span> weapon damage plus <span class="d3-color-green">300%</span> of your shield Block Chance as Holy damage.</p> <p>Requires <span class="value">Shield</span></p> <p class="special">Secondary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>2</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},shieldglare:{a:'<p>Blinded enemies take <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> more damage for <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>12</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Enemies caught in the glare have a <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> chance to be charmed and fight for you for <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>18</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Enemies with health lower than <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span> have a <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> chance to explode when Blinded, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span> weapon damage to enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>41</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">9</span> Wrath for each enemy Blinded.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>28</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Enemies hit by the glare are Slowed by <span class="d3-color-green">80%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>51</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"hol",b:"hol",c:"phy",d:"hol",e:"hol",x:"hol"},icon:1440729579,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1440729579\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">12</span> seconds</p><p>Light erupts from your shield, Blinding all enemies up to <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> yards in front of you for <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds.</p> <p>Requires <span class="value">Shield</span></p> <p class="special">Defensive</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>4</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},slash:{a:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">1%</span> increased Attack Speed for every enemy hit for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds. This effect stacks up to <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> times.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>47</em>.</p>',b:'<p>The slash becomes pure lightning and has a <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span> chance to stun enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>9</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Slash gains <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> increased Critical Hit Chance.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>34</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Carve a larger area in front of you, increasing the number of enemies hit.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>18</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">5%</span> increased armor for each enemy hit. This effect stacks up to <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> times.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>54</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"hol",b:"lit",c:"fir",d:"fir",e:"fir",x:"fir"},icon:3666483739,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3666483739\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Generate:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> Wrath per attack</p><p>Ignite the air in front of you, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">230%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p class="special">Primary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>3</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},smite:{a:'<p>The chains bind those they hit, causing them to share one another\'s fate. Enemies who share fate will be stunned for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds if they move <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> yards away from each other.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>57</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Enemies hit by the chains have a <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> chance to be Immobilized in place for <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>20</em>.</p>',c:'<p>The holy chains explode dealing <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span> weapon damage as Holy to enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>14</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">6437</span> increased Life regeneration for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds for every enemy hit by the chains. This effect stacks up to <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> times.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>51</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Increase the number of additional enemies hit to <span class="d3-color-green">5</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>37</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"lit",b:"hol",c:"hol",d:"hol",e:"hol",x:"hol"},icon:622736444,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/622736444\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Generate:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> Wrath per attack</p><p>Smite enemies up to <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> yards away with holy chains that deal <span class="d3-color-green">175%</span> weapon damage as Holy. The chains break off and strike up to <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> additional enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> yards for <span class="d3-color-green">150%</span> weapon damage as Holy.</p> <p class="special">Primary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>11</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},steedcharge:{a:'<p>The war horse deals <span class="d3-color-green">500%</span> of your Thorns every second to enemies through which you ride.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>19</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Increase the duration to <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>42</em>.</p>',c:'<p>While riding the war horse, you recover <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> of your maximum Life.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>36</em>.</p>',d:'<p>The war horse is engulfed in righteous fire, scorching all who cross its path for <span class="d3-color-green">550%</span> weapon damage per second as Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>25</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Bind <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> monsters near you with chains and drag them as you ride, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">185%</span> weapon damage as Holy every second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>52</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"fir",e:"hol",x:"phy"},icon:1510491007,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1510491007\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">16</span> seconds</p><p>Mount a celestial war horse that allows you to ride through enemies unhindered for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p> <p class="special">Utility</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>13</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},sweepattack:{a:'<p>Enemies caught in the sweep are pulled toward you.</p><p>Sweep Attack\'s damage turns into Holy.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>45</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Enemies hit by the attack will catch on fire for <span class="d3-color-green">120%</span> weapon damage over <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>11</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Heal for <span class="d3-color-green">5364</span> Life for each enemy hit.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>33</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Enemies hit by the sweep attack have a <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> chance to be tripped and Stunned for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>19</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Sweep Attack increases your Armor by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>55</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"hol",b:"fir",c:"phy",d:"lit",e:"hol",x:"phy"},icon:2186888616,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2186888616\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> Wrath</p><p>Sweep a mystical flail through enemies up to <span class="d3-color-green">18</span> yards before you, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">480%</span> weapon damage.</p> <p>Requires <span class="value">Weapon</span></p> <p class="special">Secondary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>5</em>.</p> </div> </div>'}},DiabloCalc.passivetips.crusader={blunt:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/4041733339\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Increase the damage of Justice and Blessed Hammer by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>65</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">Let your hammer educate the heathens in the error of their ways.</div> </div>',divinefortress:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1275320813\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Your Armor is increased by a percent equal to your shield\'s Block Chance.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>30</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"His shield whirled around him, faster than the eye could follow, creating an impenetrable barrier against his foes."—The Tale of Joryn</div> </div>',fanaticism:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/4037170909\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Increase the attack speed of Punish, Slash, Smite and Justice by <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>20</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"My words are not new. The ancients embraced the Light completely, and it made them mightier than we can even imagine."—Akarat</div> </div>',fervor:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2531171338\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>While wielding a <span class="d3-color-green">one-handed weapon</span>, your attack speed is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> and all cooldowns are reduced by <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>10</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"As the wicked fall at your feet, you shall know the power of the crusade."—Sir Gyrfalcon the Swift</div> </div>',finery:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3553083011\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">1.5%</span> Strength for every gem socketed into your gear.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>60</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">As you meditate upon those stones that contain the Light, you will find the Light within yourself.</div> </div>',heavenlystrength:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2960727425\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>You can wield a <span class="d3-color-green">two-handed weapon</span> in your main hand while bearing a shield in your off hand.</p><p>Your damage dealt is reduced by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>10</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"You must quiet both mind and body in order to feel the Light.  Only then shall it unleash your hidden strength."—Cleric Akkhan</div> </div>',holdyourground:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3215582651\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>You can no longer Dodge, but your Block Chance is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">30%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>40</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"I shall not be moved. Your blows cannot touch me."—Harrel the Unbreakable</div> </div>',holycause:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2633328419\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>The amount of damage dealt by your weapon is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span>.</p><p>Whenever you deal Holy damage, you heal up to <span class="d3-color-green">1%</span> of your total Life.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>27</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"Unleash your might upon the wicked that they may be cleansed."—Melmoth, the Wanderer of the Wastes</div> </div>',indestructible:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1099393495\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>When you receive fatal damage, you instead become immune to damage, gain <span class="d3-color-green">35%</span> increased damage and gain <span class="d3-color-green">107284</span> Life per Kill for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p><p>This effect may occur once every <span class="d3-color-green">60</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>25</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"As my life drained away, I could no longer feel the blows raining down upon me."—Anajinn</div> </div>',insurmountable:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3955299278\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Blocking an attack generates <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> Wrath.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>20</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">Tenacity is measured by one\'s endurance against overwhelming odds.</div> </div>',ironmaiden:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2503653692\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Your Thorns is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>50</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">Woe to those who would approach a true crusader while carrying anger in their hearts, for soon, they shall be no more.</div> </div>',longarmofthelaw:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/510878592\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Increase the duration of the Active effect of all Laws by <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>45</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"The Light sustains the law, for without it, the law is naught but empty words"—Cleric Akkhan</div> </div>',lordcommander:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3252339261\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>The cooldown of Steed Charge is reduced by <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span> and Bombardment by <span class="d3-color-green">35%</span>.</p><p>Damage dealt by Phalanx is increased <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>35</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"You will follow, or you will fall."—Kassar</div> </div>',renewal:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3449330660\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Whenever you successfully block, you gain <span class="d3-color-green">16093</span> Life.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>55</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"I say unto you, let not the foul darkness engulf the Light within you. For whosoever hears these words and knows them to be true shall be reborn."—Akarat </div> </div>',righteousness:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1833271637\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Your primary skills generate an additional <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> Wrath.</p><p>Increase maximum Wrath by <span class="d3-color-green">30</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>16</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">The deeper your belief, the greater your power.</div> </div>',toweringshield:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2754902014\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Increase the damage of Punish, Shield Bash and Blessed Shield by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span>.</p><p>Reduce the cooldown of Shield Glare by <span class="d3-color-green">30%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>70</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">A crusader\'s shield is one with his body.</div> </div>',vigilant:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/4057131540\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Increase Life regeneration by <span class="d3-color-green">2682</span>.</p><p>Reduce all non-Physical damage taken by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>13</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"May Akarat protect me and grant me the faith to allow the Light to heal my soul."—The Crusader\'s Oath</div> </div>',wrathful:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3031537987\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Each point of Wrath spent heals you for <span class="d3-color-green">1341</span> Life.</p><p>Heal amount is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">1%</span> of your Health Globe Healing Bonus.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>30</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"One clad in the Light absorbs the anger of her foes and then turns it against them."—Crusader saying</div> </div>'};